00:19:18,750 --> 00:19:24,160
 Who did I want to receive love from?  
 ♫  for those words  ♫

178
00:19:24,160 --> 00:19:26,920
 My dad?   
 ♫  The wandering wind  ♫

179
00:19:26,920 --> 00:19:30,860
 All these guys?   
 ♫  I can freely say   ♫

180
00:19:30,860 --> 00:19:33,040
 My friends?

181
00:19:33,040 --> 00:19:40,430
 Or... Si Ho?  
 ♫  The spring I'm waiting for  ♫

182
00:19:40,430 --> 00:19:44,730
 Before I receive love, I wasn't ready to give love.   
 ♫  I'm here now   ♫

183
00:19:44,730 --> 00:19:47,360
♫  Don't let me go  ♫

184
00:19:50,480 --> 00:19:55,450
♫  I barely put my head down  ♫

185
00:19:57,720 --> 00:20:00,330
♫  Give me the first greeting of spring  ♫

186
00:20:00,330 --> 00:20:08,400
 I have to go back to the place where everything began.

187
00:20:12,660 --> 00:20:15,860
 Dear X Who Doesn't Love Me  
  ♫  This heart   ♫

188
00:20:15,860 --> 00:20:17,870
 I wanted to be loved  
  ♫  until the day it breaks   ♫

189
00:20:17,870 --> 00:20:20,980
 Ever since that early morning when no one embraced me.

190
00:20:20,980 --> 00:20:25,910
 I don't deserve to be loved like that.  
  ♫  I'll give you the gift of a blue romance  ♫

191
00:20:25,910 --> 00:20:30,970
 Don't push yourself into a corner like that. You're doing your best, Hui Su.  
  ♫   Break me   ♫

